msg: Added support for non-serialized status to mark items as defective or on-hold and exclude them form the inventory reservation and issuance services; enhanced inventory counting services to consider only non serialized items with an empty status (i.e. exclude on-hold or damaged items) but also added the statusId field so that it is possible to count on-hold or damaged items.
